{"tid":110423,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【童年回憶MV】日文Butterfly配埋中文歌詞","createTime":"2017-02-06T16:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T12:37:09.000Z","uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de4bf395ce9288a04e29e9dbed327cffcd149ffb","tid":110423,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"最近整合左一條Video，將Butterfly配番中文歌詞，再配入一段Video入黎。好多童年回憶，比大家睇下，希望大家鐘意都可以Share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dreamersofhongkong/videos/1101574733302899/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdreamersofhongkong%2Fvideos%2F1101574733302899%2F&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=edabe5da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dreamersofhongkong/videos/1101574733302899/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Ac2Yl7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FAc2Yl7.png&h=dcaa64e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCredits: <br />\n作詞、作曲：千綿偉功 <br />\n編曲：渡部チェル <br />\n演唱：和田光司 <br />\n短片：bilibili <br />\n翻譯： 紅葉亭 - 樂多日誌 <br />\n<br />\n其實呢，剪呢條片都係因為我開左個叫【一個發夢的地方 Dreamers of Hong Kong】既Page，好希望大家可以知道下，如果鐘意就Follow一下，同埋隨意交流一下你既寶貴意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/pmiJ5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FpmiJ5n.png&h=eceafc1a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想係呢度同大家介紹呢個Page既原因係因為眼白白見住眼前呢個社會有好多好多唔同既問題， 政府一連串既問題唔在講，甚至見到呢個社會既風氣，都慢慢因為大家要搵空間生存而扭曲哂.. <br />\n<br />\n我好想好想慢慢去改變呢一個地方。 <br />\n<br />\n係有限既資源同人力之下，我開左呢個Facebook Page，好想係呢個地方鼓勵大家係香港我地都可以去發夢。我好相信好相信我地每個人心中都有大大小小唔同既夢想，所以我地好想好想去收集呢啲夢想，再去同大家分享，一方面幫人去追夢，二黎希望呢啲分享可以鼓勵到大家都去發夢。 <br />\n<br />\n至於呢個Page既運作模式呢，其實係想Recruit一班唔同Background既人入去， 咁當我地有好多人支持之後，個Page就會有好多唔同Background既人會係入面。 情況就好似係一個大Platform咁（或者可以話係好似呢到咁，好犀利咩人都有...） <br />\n<br />\n當我地去收集左一個個既夢想之後，就好希望有相關經驗既大家可以比下意見同方向，等迷失左唔知點行第一步既大家，都可以快啲易啲咁向住自己既夢想去出發。 <br />\n<br />\n真係好希望好希望呢到既大家，如果你都支持呢個理念，可以支持我地，一齊努力諗計仔去幫下身邊既大家！<br />\n<br />\n多謝你睇到最尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40e990d41dc861f2f30befc7e65e321583f8783","tid":110423,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"推一推先，希望見到既你會支持一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fd94e5a9a147f38f12915e430bf2962e8d7ff7","tid":110423,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"再推一推先，希望多啲人可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該唒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d916e3cfe0bb97c4b2b2eb4d07f954e81ece27","tid":110423,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"真係今晚最後一推，希望大家見到會睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1096d8683157fad1dc8f1ff74c722ccdf5cf553b","tid":110423,"uid":78922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已like"},{"pid":"b711c4b3786b8cc5e693030f36cd4ddc6cd5a412","tid":110423,"uid":9160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69b9cf93712f856f157231e6eb4e26ec70c3eab4","tid":110423,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"第一段有d位歌詞變左第二段，<br />\n例如nanimonai yononakaja 變左yarusenai yononakaja，之後itoshii個句又變左常識。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d07201147682522eae01fc02dafe2e823c1b32","tid":1104